name: Ever Fallen In Love (With Someone You Shouldn't've?)
description:
"And if I start a commotion
I run the risk of losing you
And that's worse
Ever fallen in love? (Love…)
In love with someone
You shouldn't've fallen in love with"

That song was coming from the greatest punk rock band called Buzzcocks (RIP Pete Shelley), which inspire me to make this works.

Meanwhile, there is a story about a one-sided love that has been going on for more than three years, Sometimes made me fun and also always has a painful situation. 

fuck it's time to move
